{"tid":137122,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"新垣結衣(54)以同一個地方為目標在天空中飛翔這就是元素 像我和你一樣","createTime":"2017-02-27T14:43:27.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-27T15:15:28.000Z","uid":51905,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c18821fceb81ec2c8b8be422e8f957fd6f33f624","tid":137122,"uid":51905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T14:43:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><blockquote>▼▼▼▼▼▼▼▼▼▼▼▼▼▼▼▼▼<br />\n- 全舊post連結：<a href=\"https://goo.gl/nP47fu\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FnP47fu&d=YoMLTdJ4KFDt7wuWjEYT14zZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=92c6da4e\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/nP47fu</a><br />\n- <span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>2樓新手入門攻略、投票參考<br />\nGoogle drive綜合下載&amp;常見問題</strong></span><br />\n- 3樓新劇資訊、相集、巴打創作<br />\n- 4樓綜藝、專訪、相關影片<br />\n長都一定要睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 爬晒先好黎問野<br />\n-新post格式：<a href=\"https://goo.gl/1jRJUk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2F1jRJUk&d=YoMLTdJ4KFDt7wuWjEYT14zZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=0fc42f27\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/1jRJUk</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\"><strong>溫馨提示</strong></span></span><br />\n - <span style=\"color: red;\">如果有人搞事可以自動波扑佢</span><br />\n- 睇完2樓google後 小心唔好講禁語<br />\n-唔洗怕醜盡情出聲 柒左笑你係基本<br />\n-有咩相關新資源可以擺上黎<br />\n-頭post出齊先好留名 記得正皮<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/20/221937_c5ee0ef1b3d3c76b614b20da3f6f6220.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F20%2F221937_c5ee0ef1b3d3c76b614b20da3f6f6220.gif&h=33a27c85&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲▲▲▲▲▲▲▲▲▲▲▲▲▲▲▲▲</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>標題來源：<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/27/224310_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F27%2F224310_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=3edf92d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n[img]<a href=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/27/224316_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F27%2F224316_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5&d=YoMLTdJ4KFDt7wuWjEYT14zZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=91a6e829\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/27/224316_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5</a></strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>上年秋季新劇<br />\n《逃避雖可恥但有用》</strong></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/CsPghtrVMAA-YH5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FCsPghtrVMAA-YH5.jpg&h=1a00743c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n官網：<a href=\"http://www.tbs.co.jp/NIGEHAJI_tbs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.tbs.co.jp%2FNIGEHAJI_tbs&d=YoMLTdJ4KFDt7wuWjEYT14zZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=9f45f851\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.tbs.co.jp/NIGEHAJI_tbs</a><br />\nFB：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/nigehaji.tbs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fnigehaji.tbs&d=YoMLTdJ4KFDt7wuWjEYT14zZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=6e3a43d0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/nigehaji.tbs</a><br />\nTwitter：<a href=\"https://twitter.com/nigehaji_tbs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fnigehaji_tbs&d=YoMLTdJ4KFDt7wuWjEYT14zZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=cc55fce8\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/nigehaji_tbs</a><br />\nIG：<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/nigehajigram\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fnigehajigram&d=YoMLTdJ4KFDt7wuWjEYT14zZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=04d76924\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/nigehajigram</a><br />\n預告片：<a href=\"https://youtu.be/nM2MAx6_65Y\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FnM2MAx6_65Y&d=YoMLTdJ4KFDt7wuWjEYT14zZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=b8b73978\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/nM2MAx6_65Y</a><br />\n <br />\n出演：<br />\n新垣結衣/星野源/大谷亮平/藤井隆<br />\n真野惠里菜/成田凌/山賀琴子/宇梶剛士<br />\n富田靖子/古田新太/石田百和子<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/10/14/233547_f50f852bf9aab8e759504ba6f724920d.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F10%2F14%2F233547_f50f852bf9aab8e759504ba6f724920d.gif&h=44cdcd3a&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/10/15/185308_aad906a54864ad5e19c4c7c30c6216d2.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F10%2F15%2F185308_aad906a54864ad5e19c4c7c30c6216d2.gif&h=b1ff0dd8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n主題曲：星野 源 - 「恋」<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/jhOVibLEDhA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FjhOVibLEDhA&d=YoMLTdJ4KFDt7wuWjEYT14zZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=cec52f21\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/jhOVibLEDhA</a><br />\n恋ダンス 教學片<br />\n<a href=\"http://youtu.be/MOyGxzG91yo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FMOyGxzG91yo&d=YoMLTdJ4KFDt7wuWjEYT14zZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=51f7e4ae\" target=\"_blank\">http://youtu.be/MOyGxzG91yo</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/CsPUakUVMAEaIm9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FCsPUakUVMAEaIm9.jpg&h=ff57ed82&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/CufWpTsXgAE8r5D.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FCufWpTsXgAE8r5D.jpg&h=e6f7af0b&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n　　女星新垣結衣接拍十月開播TBS日劇《逃避雖可恥但有用》，飾演像上班一樣為特定目的結婚的新妻，劇集根據海野津波在月刊《Kiss》連載的同名漫畫改編，以&ldquo;丈夫是雇主，妻子是職員&rdquo;的價值觀為基礎，講述契約結婚的主人公的故事。<br />\n<br />\n　　劇中新垣結衣飾演主人公森山，這位25歲愛妄想的女子沒有男友，畢業後沒有工作，做派遣職員沒公司用，生活不順終日煩惱，她幫單身職員津崎做家務，對方提出不如像上班一樣結婚，於是他們秘密定下契約，開始了&ldquo;丈夫是雇主，妻子是職員&rdquo;的新婚生活。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>分析文(含劇透)<br />\n《逃恥》：厭世地擁抱生命中的缺憾</strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.thenewslens.com/article/59675\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.thenewslens.com%2Farticle%2F59675&d=YoMLTdJ4KFDt7wuWjEYT14zZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=530a06ed\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.thenewslens.com/article/59675</a><br />\n<br />\n《逃恥》橫掃91回學院賞<br />\n[url]<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/h2TnKc2.png[/url\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fh2TnKc2.png%5B%2Furl&d=YoMLTdJ4KFDt7wuWjEYT14zZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=b9db357f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://i.imgur.com/h2TnKc2.png[/url</a></blockquote>"},{"pid":"48d29b5f0a244fd8ffbefba9b30b63a0332b36cc","tid":137122,"uid":51905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T14:43:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>新手上路主線攻略：</strong></span></span><br />\n一定要睇：逃恥、今日子、飛翔、legal high、code blue、父女、mbmh<br />\n<br />\n可睇可唔睇：S警官、亂馬、龍櫻、辣妹、涉谷15、 smile<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">唔撚洗睇：全開(自行google男主)</span><br />\n<br />\n分支：綜藝(4樓)、專訪、電影、CM、劇集特典<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: green;\">LIHKG投票參考：</span></strong><br />\n<blockquote><span style=\"color: pink;\"><strong>最喜愛結衣出演的作品(可修改)</strong></span><br />\n投票：<a href=\"https://goo.gl/01H8Cy\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2F01H8Cy&d=YoMLTdJ4KFDt7wuWjEYT14zZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=db7ffa5f\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/01H8Cy</a><br />\n結果：<a href=\"https://goo.gl/ctqRQJ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FctqRQJ&d=YoMLTdJ4KFDt7wuWjEYT14zZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=66627b46\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/ctqRQJ</a><br />\n<br />\n投票方法：最鍾意既揀1，如此類推，冇睇過果D唔洗揀<br />\n計分方法：當你睇左7套，你排第1果套會有7分、第7套1分、冇睇過0分<br />\n如果你睇得3套，第1果套就得3分<br />\n咁係結果到就會睇到越高分就係越受歡迎<br />\n大家補番果陣就可以有個參考<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\"><strong>最喜愛結衣出演的角色(可修改)</strong></span><br />\n投票：<a href=\"https://goo.gl/Ja83Fv\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FJa83Fv&d=YoMLTdJ4KFDt7wuWjEYT14zZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=898310f5\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/Ja83Fv</a><br />\n結果：<a href=\"https://goo.gl/wQTo2C\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FwQTo2C&d=YoMLTdJ4KFDt7wuWjEYT14zZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=aefecbdd\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/wQTo2C</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\"><strong>最喜愛的螢幕情侶(可修改)</strong></span><br />\n投票：<a href=\"https://goo.gl/Dqcmh2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FDqcmh2&d=YoMLTdJ4KFDt7wuWjEYT14zZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=e3227112\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/Dqcmh2</a><br />\n結果：<a href=\"https://goo.gl/slzFiE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FslzFiE&d=YoMLTdJ4KFDt7wuWjEYT14zZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=463bf87c\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/slzFiE</a><br />\n</blockquote><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: green;\">基本小知識：</span></strong><br />\n日本無分男 / 女主角呢樣野<br />\n得一個主演，好少會有雙主演<br />\n例如結衣係主演，星野源就要係助演<br />\n<br />\n~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>綜合下載(由星空巴提供)</strong></span></span><br />\n隔離登pm gmail比「星空下的緣份」巴打等批<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>現時bd版lh有既新畫面係無字幕<br />\n要字幕完整請選擇1080i(無bd版新畫面)</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n常見問題：<br />\n<br />\nQ：我想問星空巴個drive入面既片點整字幕<br />\nA：Down片+字幕落黎，將片+字幕改成同一檔名，Down「media player classic」落黎播條片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nQ：點解我down唔到Google drive啲片？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />點解會顯示禁止or 失敗？係咪星空巴Off左條link？<br />\nA：人在Link在，解決方法有兩個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n1) 用其他Browser再試下Down<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n2) 將你想Down嘅片滑鼠右click加上<span style=\"color: red;\">星號</span>，之後去番自己個Google drive入面，click<span style=\"color: red;\">星號標記</span>，你會見到你岩岩加左星號嘅片，再右click禁<span style=\"color: red;\">建立副本</span>。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n做完以上步驟，條片就會自動加到你自己嘅Google drive<br />\nps：你個drive剩餘容量要多過條片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">如果都係唔得呢？</span><br />\n唯有俾多次email星空巴再share<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"c60e9b669ab5fce2a78e762dfb230443680a0d3f","tid":137122,"uid":51905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T14:44:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>2017年3月新SP：「羈絆～奔跑吧!奇蹟的小馬～」</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/CqgU-iuUAAAVfRR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FCqgU-iuUAAAVfRR.jpg&h=9e1a2695&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/CqnVjUjUkAEAwP0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FCqnVjUjUkAEAwP0.jpg&h=b5b8805c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nNHK特集電視劇「羈絆～奔跑吧!奇蹟的小馬～」出演決定了！<br />\n<br />\n　　本作品，是東日本大震災受傷的一家，各種困難和戰鬥的同時，地震日出生的小馬夢想的賽馬到成長的身姿，福島縣的相馬舞台壓倒性的描繪的SP電視劇。<br />\n<br />\n新垣結衣，飾演松下家的長女---松下將子役。<br />\n<br />\n　　東日本大地震失去了長子的拓馬（岡田將生）的家人，和地震當日出生的小馬相依為命。父親&middot;雅之（役所廣司）和長女&middot;將子（新垣結衣）想將死去的哥哥夢見的競技馬培育起來，母親&middot;佳世子（田中裕子）沉浸在失去了長子的悲痛之中無法自拔。以前是騎手的青年&middot;夏雄（勝地涼）與協助他家人，進行受災地的複興，同時也依靠著作為北海道的牧場主人的加山（小林薰）。於是家庭面臨嚴峻的現實。真的是楊是夢寐以求的競技馬就能夠跑起來嗎？<br />\n<br />\n《電視劇概要》<br />\n廣播：NHK 2017年3月23及24日兩晚（前後篇&middot;各73分）<br />\n演出：役所広司、新垣結衣、岡田將生、勝地涼、小林薫、田中裕子<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">新垣結衣x瑛太W主演映畫「ミックス。」(混合雙打)<br />\n挑戰乒乓球題材的浪漫喜劇！ </strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/97B91eP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F97B91eP.jpg&h=61a86686&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4TB523R.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4TB523R.jpg&h=c72bb608&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n腳本：古沢良太（Legal High 腳本） <br />\n監督：石川淳一（Legal High 監督） <br />\n<br />\n共演卡司：広末涼子、遠藤憲一、田中美佐子、佐野勇斗、瀬戸康史、永野芽郁、蒼井優、森崎博之、吉田鋼太郎、生瀬勝久、山口紗彌加、斎藤司、久間田琳加、鈴木福、谷花音、真木よう子、小日向文世等。 <br />\n<br />\n　　2月中旬開始攝影，2017年秋全國東寶系公開！ 新垣結衣飾演戀愛和工作都很失敗的原天才乒乓球少女、快30歲的單身OL富田多滿子，與瑛太飾演的原日本職業拳擊手組合成乒乓球混雙，向全國大賽挑戰的故事。<br />\n<br />\n~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">相集</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n擺圖用google drive：<a href=\"https://goo.gl/qXk2TG\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FqXk2TG&d=YoMLTdJ4KFDt7wuWjEYT14zZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=3edc89e7\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/qXk2TG</a><br />\n(已整合隔離巴打多年黎既圖)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/hz4x109m\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fhz4x109m&h=9ce12743&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9464Ee2.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9464Ee2.gif&h=3404fea8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n巴打創作：<a href=\"https://goo.gl/mnrGKF\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FmnrGKF&d=YoMLTdJ4KFDt7wuWjEYT14zZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=5e48828e\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/mnrGKF</a><br />\n<br />\nbinc名單：<a href=\"https://goo.gl/Eeyy7O\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FEeyy7O&d=YoMLTdJ4KFDt7wuWjEYT14zZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=8d8407a4\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/Eeyy7O</a><br />\n<br />\nios用whatsapp save gif 教學：<a href=\"https://goo.gl/EpWsmP\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FEpWsmP&d=YoMLTdJ4KFDt7wuWjEYT14zZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=64f4b6bd\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/EpWsmP</a></blockquote>"},{"pid":"9d3b5ab997dc1472e93d6cf4c515943d755c24f9","tid":137122,"uid":62635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T14:44:05.000Z","msg":"留名第一<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/27/224404_c5ee0ef1b3d3c76b614b20da3f6f6220.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F27%2F224404_c5ee0ef1b3d3c76b614b20da3f6f6220.gif&h=0f6c89e7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f1c54546a547e39b09c59c55cebc1a5a5515ff3c","tid":137122,"uid":51905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T14:44:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">綜藝、專訪、相關影片</span></span><br />\n<br />\nB站sub呢兩個up主有新野就即刻睇到<br />\n生肉：<a href=\"http://space.bilibili.com/390868/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fspace.bilibili.com%2F390868%2F&d=YoMLTdJ4KFDt7wuWjEYT14zZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=e98b6cef\" target=\"_blank\">http://space.bilibili.com/390868/</a><br />\n熟肉：<a href=\"http://space.bilibili.com/16918352/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fspace.bilibili.com%2F16918352%2F&d=YoMLTdJ4KFDt7wuWjEYT14zZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=5836a0d9\" target=\"_blank\">http://space.bilibili.com/16918352/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s23.postimg.org/g2p80f3xn/image.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs23.postimg.org%2Fg2p80f3xn%2Fimage.jpg&h=de5a979b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/L65E0uC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FL65E0uC.jpg&h=c72ed5e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2016 紅白審查專區<br />\n新垣結衣全鏡頭：<a href